     C                     END
     C                     LEAVE
     C                     ELSE
     C                     Z-ADDF2CHGD    W@KDT
     C           K#AGD     KLIST
     C                     KFLD           W@KDTY
     C                     KFLD           W@KDTM
     C                     KFLD           W@KDTD
     C           K#AGD     CHAINAGDPL12              97
